---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Terms & Conditions"
	description="Terms and conditions for Balance Performance Physiotherapy."
>
	<PageHero
		title="&amp; Conditions"
		highlight="Terms"
		breadcrumb="Terms &amp; Conditions"
	/>
	<section class="rich-content">
		<div class="container">
			<p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>
			<p>These terms govern your use of our clinic services and this website. By booking an appointment or using this site, you agree to these terms.</p>

			<h2>Appointments and cancellations</h2>
			<p>Appointments cancelled with less than 24 hours' notice may incur a charge equivalent to the full appointment fee. Please let us know as early as possible if you need to reschedule.</p>

			<h2>Payment</h2>
			<p>Payment is due at the time of appointment unless otherwise agreed. We accept all major credit and debit cards. Invoices for insurance claims are issued on request.</p>

			<h2>Insurance</h2>
			<p>We're recognised by major insurers including Bupa and AXA PPP Health. Please check your cover with your insurer before booking. You remain responsible for any shortfall.</p>

			<h2>Clinical information</h2>
			<p>Information on this site is provided for general guidance only and is not a substitute for professional clinical assessment. Always consult a qualified clinician before acting on information you read online.</p>

			<h2>Intellectual property</h2>
			<p>All content on this site, text, images, logos, is owned by Balance Performance Physiotherapy or its licensors and protected by copyright.</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:enquiries@balancephysio.com">enquiries@balancephysio.com</a>.</p>

			<p><em>This placeholder content should be replaced with terms reviewed by your legal advisor before launch.</em></p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
